A method is intended to return the average of the positive values in an array. The array contains at least one positive value.

```java
public static double averagePositive(int[] data)
{
    int sum = 0;
    int count = 0;

    for (int value : data)
    {
        if (value > 0)
        {
            sum += value;
            count++;
        }
    }

    return sum / count;
}
```

